data.description: Explore this distinctive country home just a short walk from Norris Lake, offering stunning mountain views on a peaceful cul-de-sac. The main level includes a master bedroom with an attached bath and a spacious living room. The rear deck, adjacent to the kitchen and dining area, is perfect for gatherings. The covered front porch provides a mountain view and a serene setting.This newly renovated 2-story, 3BR/2+BA home has great short-term rental potential. The buyer can occupy the primary section while possibly renting out the lower-level third bedroom. The lower level is equipped as a full studio apartment with plumbing and a separate entrance, offering flexibility and investment potential. Don't miss this opportunity!
